<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Marriage&amp;action=edit&amp;section=34" title="Edit section: Related concepts">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Related concepts</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Adultery" title="Adultery">Adultery</a> - Sexual intercourse between a married person and a partner other than the lawful spouse.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Alimony" title="Alimony">Alimony</a> - obligation of support.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Annulment" title="Annulment">Annulment</a> - legal procedure for declaring a marriage null and void.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Aufruf" title="Aufruf">Aufruf</a> - A ceremony in which Jews pelt the couple to be married with candy on the <a href="/wiki/Shabbat" title="Shabbat">Shabbat</a> before the wedding.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Betrothal" title="Betrothal">Betrothal</a> - formal state of engagement to be married.</li>
